WEBVTT

00:09.871 --> 00:11.209
(exclaiming)

00:15.568 --> 00:17.068
(school bell ringing)

00:20.856 --> 00:22.257
(Barney belches)

00:22.291 --> 00:24.960
(tires screech)

00:24.994 --> 00:26.194
D'oh!

00:26.228 --> 00:27.495
(tires screeching)

00:27.530 --> 00:29.164
(grunts)

00:29.198 --> 00:31.633
(gentle orchestral
music playing)

